nals *when* the first mismatch occurs, overriding the original hint display structure, while retaining the error counts.\n\n6. **Syntax Advice:** Ensure all signals are declared with appropriate types (`logic` or `reg`). The original TB uses many implicit assignments; I will ensure clarity. The final output structure must be strictly followed.",
